V2.21 (17.3.2007): (english)

 - added some more sub-commands to GETINFO ARexx command

    - for retrieving SV module major versions)
    - for retrieving number of SV modules/types per category
    - for retrieving names of SV modules (and save types)
    - for retreiving graphics properties (gfxalpha)

    see "ARexx-Scripts/GetInfo.rx" for usage demo

 - fixed several bugs in the [CTA] code dealing with
   names (and related extensions) of modules ending /w
   .sv5object/.sv5driver/.sv5operator

