V2.13 (9.2.2007): (english)

 - it is now possible to select predefined Convolve/ConvolveNxN
   matrix definition files easily over the GUI (overriding
   custom matrix settings, if wanted); you can place your own,
   new convolution matrix files under

    ENVARC:SView5-Library/Convolve/#?.controlpad
    ENVARC:SView5-Library/ConvolveNxN/#?.controlpad

  For ConvolveNxN, the size of the matrix must be included
  in the controlpad (see sample definition files), since
  5x5, 7x7 and 9x9 are allowed (normal Convolve is 3x3)

