   were not included

V1.65 (16.5.2005): (english)

 - MorphOS: fixed MOS-specific UI hits/bugs in PNG-Box, JPEG-Box, GIF-Box
 - MorphOS: fixed problems with "e"(execution) bits in Tools directory
 - updated a few copyright strings in GUIs
 - remove keyfile code everywhere
 - officially added plugins for AdPro, ImageFX, PPaint, PageStream
 - library updated, lots of new SV5Objects (including MorphOS versions)

